block_list.body: It isn't Halloween without a Ghost or two. Learn how to fold this Origami Ghost or Reaper designed by Ladislav Kaňka (LkOrigami) & Easy Origami. This model is really cool Enjoy!!! If you would like to see the original tutorials check the links below: Ladislav Kaňka @LKorigami : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uDqaL1ph1sA @Easy Origami : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNbFcjvZpC0 Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
